<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<title>lmạ tyjy yạ ạ̹lhnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lmạ tyjy yạ ạ̹lhnạ .. bḥḍwrk fy wsṭnạ
 yrtfʿ yạ yswʿ mạ bynạ .. wnlms ạlḥḍwr brwḥnạ
 wạldẖbạỷḥ ttrfʿ lk .. yạ yswʿ ạlmjd lyk
 klmẗ mnk rby tḥyy .. kl qlb bynạdyk
 ạlqrạr- mḥtạjyn lk
 lmsẗ mnk .. tjbr ạlqlb ạlksyr
 tḥḍn ạltạyh tḍmh .. ttftḥ ʿyn ạlḍryr
 mḥtạjyn lk
 2- wf ḥḍwrk yjy nwrk .. wạlẓlạm tnhy zmạnh
 ntmly bslṭạn klạmk .. wạlʿdw yrjʿ mkạnh
 mạ fy slṭạn wlạ qwẗ .. gẖyr lsẖkẖṣk fy ạlwsṭ
 tmlạ tsẖbʿ wtnwr .. kl qlb byk ạ̹rtbṭ
 3- ạ̹dẖạ sẖwfnạ rby mjdk .. nʿrf ạ̹n wḥdk kfạyẗ
 yṣgẖr ạlʿạlm fy ʿynạ .. wrạḥ nsẖwf klh nfạyẗ
 bạlmrạḥm ạ̹smʿ ṣrạkẖnạ .. wạftqdnạ bạlḥnạn
 mḥtạjyn lk yạ ạ̹lhnạ .. ạ̹rsl ạlrwḥ fyḍạn</lyrics>
</song>